overview: When Dr. Nihilus threatens to destroy the world with his M.E.A.T.L.O.A.F. device, unstoppable super spy Tim Possible and his trusty butler Prufrock are called in to put a stop to Nihilus's plan and save the world. That being said, Tim quickly realizes that this "one last mission" is a lot more than he bargained for.
title: Meatloaf
